                <div class="Item-BodyWrap">
                    <div class="Item-Body">
                        <div class="Message">
                            Hi Masterne0,<br /><br />The WiFi one has been tough to find a consistent relation to any setting, configuration, or method to resolve it.&nbsp; We have escalated that one, but since the developers can't recreate the issue, they can't find a cause, and can't resolve it.&nbsp; I'm still gathering data and trying to find a common link that I can give them to get to the bottom of it.<br /><br />The unknown device notification is a new one, and I haven't seen that message before recently, so I'm thinking the message must not have many triggers.&nbsp; That should narrow the scope for the developers to find the cause and resolve it.&nbsp; I have seen others saying the same thing, and only recently, so I do think there may be a bug, and I am escalating the issue.&nbsp; Hopefully we'll have a software update to fix it asap.<br /><br />Thanks for the detailed info, it will help in the escalation,<br />~Ryan                        </div>
